    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>회원가입</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css" />
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <h1>회원가입</h1>
    </header>
    <section>
        <form id="sign_up_form" action="survey.html" method="post">
            <div class="form-group">
                <label>이름: </label>
                <input id="name" type="text">
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
                <label>이메일: </label>
                <input id="email" type="email">
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
                <label>비밀번호: </label>
                <input id="pw" type="password">
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
                <label>비밀번호 확인: </label>
                <input id="pw_check" type="password">
            </div>

            <button type="submit" onClick="location.href='survey.html'">확인</button>
        </form>
    </section>
</body>
</html>


1. 부모 요소에 display: flex 주기
.form-group {
    display: flex;
}

2. label한테 고정 너비 주기
.form-group label {
    width: 120px;
}

3. input한테 남는 공간 차지하게 만들기
.form-group input {
    flex: 1;
}

4. 전체 폼에 padding, margin 주기
#sign_up_form {
    border: 1px solid black;
    padding: 20px;
    width: 400px;
    margin: 0 auto;
}

5. 입력칸 꾸미기 (선택사항)
.form-group input {
    padding: 8px;
    border: 1px solid #ccc;
    border-radius: 4px;
}







